NAME
    df - report file system disk space usage

SYNOPSIS
    df [OPTION]... [FILE]...

DESCRIPTION
    df displays the amount of disk space available on the file system
    containing each file name argument. If no file name is given, the space
    available on all currently mounted file systems is shown.
    Disk space is shown in 1K blocks by default.


OPTIONS
    Show information about the file system on which each FILE resides, or all
    file systems by default.

    -h, --human-readable
        print sizes in powers of 1024 (e.g., 1023M)

    -T, --print-type
        print file system type

    --help display this help and exit

